There&#39;s no built-in capability to verify that content matches certain 
specs. In fact, Heritrix tries to be as tolerant as web browsers in 
accepting content that might have valuable outlinks to crawl.

It would be a small and easy bit of code to add, though -- just one more 
step in the post-fetch processing of a retrieved document.

- Gordon @ IA

